==Culture==
:1. A [[language]] of [[Kyrgyzstan]].  
:2. Turkish [[ethnic group]] in Kyrgyzstan.

===Etymology===
:1. Male [[given name]] meaning "stalker" or "hunter". (Arabic)
:2. [[Given name]] meaning "imperishable", "inextinguishable", or "undying". (Turkish) Variations include [[Kirgiz]] and [[Kyrgyz]].